yk|Melnyk Racing Stables]]\n|1:38.99\n|-\n|align=center|2008\n|[[Rahy's Attorney]]\n|align=center|4\n|[[Slade Callaghan]]\n|[[Ian Black (horseman)|Ian Black]]\n|Ellie-Boje Farm \n|1:39.53\n|-\n|align=center|2007\n||[[Eccentric (horse)|Eccentric]]\n|align=center|6\n|[[David K. Clark|David Clark]]\n|[[Roger Attfield]]\n|[[Gary A. Tanaka]]\n|1:45.05\n|-\n|align=center|2006\n|[[Remarkable News]]\n|align=center|4\n|[[Javier Castellano]]\n|[[Angel Penna, Jr.]]\n|Holly Rincon\n|1:39.67\n|-\n|align=center|2005\n|[[Le Cinquieme Essai]]\n|align=center|6\n|[[Steven Bahen]]\n|[[Paul Nielsen]]\n|William J. Scott\n|1:40.79\n|-\n|align=center|2004\n|[[Slew Valley]]\n|align=center|7\n|[[James S. McAleney|Jim McAleney]]\n|[[Reade Baker]]\n|Rich Meadow Farm (W. James Hindman)\n|1:40.24\n|-\n|align=center|2002\n|[[Quiet Resolve]]\n|align=center|7\n|[[Todd Kabel]]\n|[[Mark Frostad]]\n|[[Sam-Son Farm]]\n|1:40.88\n|-\n|align=center|2001\n|[[Red Sea (horse)|Red Sea]]\n|align=center|5\n|[[Emile Ramsammy]]\n|[[Roger Attfield]]\n|[[Prince Fahd Salman]]\n|1:47.49\n|-\n|align=center|2001\n|[[Del Mar Show]]\n|align=center|4\n|[[Robbie Davis]]\n|[[William I. Mott]]\n|[[Allen E. Paulson|Allen E. Paulson Trust]]\n|1:48.17\n|-\n|align=center|2000\n|[[Super Red]]\n|align=center|4\n|[[Emile Ramsammy]]\n|[[Malcolm Pierce]]\n|[[Stronach Stables]]\n|1:43.78\n|-\n|align=center|1999\n|[[Incitatus (horse)|Incitatus]]\n|align=center|6\n|[[Slade Callaghan]]\n|[[Ronald Burke (horse trainer)|Ronald Burke]]\n|John Kom-Tong\n|1:40.57\n|-\n|align=center|1998\n|[[Kiridashi (horse)|Kiridashi]]\n|align=center|6\n|[[Todd Kabel]]\n|[[Barbara J. Minshall]]\n|[[Minshall Farms]]\n|1:39.80\n|-\n|align=center|1997\n|[[Kiridashi (horse)|Kiridashi]]\n|align=center|5\n|[[Mickey Walls]]\n|[[Barbara J. Minshall]]\n|[[Minshall Farms]]\n|1:40.00\n|-\n|align=center|1996\n|[[Lahint]]\n|align=center|5\n|[[Todd Kabel]]\n|[[Kathy Patton-Casse]]\n|[[Harry T. Mangurian, Jr.]]\n|1:40.20\n|- \n|align=center|1995\n|[[Jet Freighter]]\n|alig